OL,3,CWest of England Mayor hints at tourism
OL,4,Ctax for Bristol and Bath
OL,6,FThe West of England Mayor has hinted
OL,7,Fvisitors to Bristol and Bath could
OL,8,Fsoon have to pay an overnight tourist
OL,9,Ftax, after the government announced
OL,10,Fplans to give regional leaders more
OL,11,Fpower to raise money locally.
OL,13,FLabour mayor Helen Godwin said
OL,14,Fproceeds from an overnight visitor
OL,15,Flevy would have "the potential to
OL,16,Fsupport and enhance the (tourism)
OL,17,Fsector's businesses and workers".
