OL,3,CWest of England Mayor hints at tourism
OL,4,Ctax for Bristol and Bath
OL,6,FAhead of the Budget on Wednesday, the
OL,7,Fgovernment confirmed reports that it
OL,8,Fwill allow England's mayors to invest
OL,9,Fin transport and infrastructure
OL,10,Fthrough a tax on tourists.
OL,12,FThe fee would apply to overnight trips
OL,13,Fat hotels, holiday lets, B&Bs and
OL,14,Fguesthouses. It would see parts of the
OL,15,FUK follow the likes of New York, Milan
OL,16,Fand Paris in charging holidaymakers
OL,17,Ffor short trips.
