OL,3,CWest of England Mayor hints at tourism
OL,4,Ctax for Bristol and Bath
OL,6,F"Residents and visitors alike know how
OL,7,Fspecial our part of the world is, from
OL,8,Four people to our culture to our
OL,9,Fnature. Tourism is now worth a record
OL,10,F#2.7 billion to the West's economy,
OL,11,Fwhich is a key industry for our new
OL,12,FGrowth Strategy over the coming
OL,13,Fdecade," said Helen Godwin.
