OL,3,CWest of England Mayor hints at tourism
OL,4,Ctax for Bristol and Bath
OL,6,F"These new powers are a real vote of
OL,7,Fconfidence in our region taking more
OL,8,Fcontrol of our future. Proceeds from
OL,9,Fan overnight visitor levy, that people
OL,10,Ffrom across the West are used to
OL,11,Fpaying on holiday ourselves, have the
OL,12,Fpotential to support and enhance the
OL,13,Fsector's businesses and workers `
OL,14,Fincluding with better transport
OL,15,Foptions."
