OL,3,CWest of England Mayor hints at tourism
OL,4,Ctax for Bristol and Bath
OL,6,FBristol City Council has similarly
OL,7,Fshowed an interest in the tax as an
OL,8,Fextra revenue source, commissioning a
OL,9,F'feasibility study' earlier this year
OL,10,Finto ways of implementing the charge.
OL,12,FSecretary of State for Housing,
OL,13,FCommunities and Local Government,
OL,14,FSteve Reed, said: "Tourists travel
OL,15,Ffrom near and far to visit England's
OL,16,Fbrilliant cities and regions.
