OL,3,CWest of England Mayor hints at tourism
OL,4,Ctax for Bristol and Bath
OL,6,F"We're giving our mayors powers to
OL,7,Fharness this and put more money into
OL,8,Flocal priorities, so they can keep
OL,9,Fdriving growth and investing in these
OL,10,Fcommunities for years to come."
OL,12,FThe criticism of such a tax is that it
OL,13,Fcould discourage overseas
OL,14,Fholidaymakers from visiting the UK and
OL,15,Feven put off Brits from taking breaks
OL,16,Fat home.
