OL,3,CWest of England Mayor hints at tourism
OL,4,Ctax for Bristol and Bath
OL,6,FUKHospitality, the trade body for
OL,7,Fhospitality businesses, has warned
OL,8,Fthat the levy would be a "lose-lose"
OL,9,Ffor businesses, drive up costs and
OL,10,Fincrease inflation.
OL,12,FBefore implementing an overnight tax
OL,13,Ffor tourists, the West of England
OL,14,FCombined Authority would need to
OL,15,Fconsult with the tourism sector and
OL,16,Fbusiness leaders.
